      "date": "2012-05-19 18:48:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f4190a9c-a1df-11e1-abdc-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
