      "date": "2012-06-08 03:44:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/cf924136-b119-11e1-8d5e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
