        "username": "Jay",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-06-08 05:49:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nIf LCT_REMEMBER is not needed, you don;t need to grab that spinlock at all.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
